name: LionCEO
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
LionCEO is a premium token provides REAL profits for our Investors. With the slogan Unleashing the Power of Memes with Real Yield, AI, GameFi, and NFTs, $LCEO is the leading reward token with LIVE utilities in the BSC ecosystem! 
The Revolutionary Meme Token
Not just a meme token, our premium token unleashes the potential of LIVE multi-AI utilities, GameFi,Staking, and NFT Generator to provide REAL profits for our investors
We're here to disrupt the norm and revolutionize the way meme coin projects work and grow. Our fully decentralized ecosystem offers unparalleled security and practicality
